English: The dogs and the dogs, even the stray dogs around the US
you don't see dogs going hungry here
because I guess we pick up stray dogs
and if they don't get collected by someone, they get put down
which is a different thing instead of just letting them roam

English: The dogs and the dogs, even the stray dogs around the US,

Chinese: 这些狗，包括美国各地的流浪狗，

input: The dogs and the dogs, even the stray dogs around the US, you don't see dogs going hungry here because I guess we pick up stray dogs and if they don't get collected by someone, they get put down, which is a different thing instead of just letting them roam.
